Why not? <br>
<br>
Shamen are taken for slow over beastlords, Enchanters are taken over Bards for crowd control, Clerics are taken over druids for healing, Rogues are taken over monks for DPS, Mages are taken over necro's ....  <br>
<br>
Why (if a value judgement has to be made) should a Warrior not be the primary choice for main tank? <br>
<br>
